oat.com/blog/2026/07/a-probabilistic-approach-to-functional-organization-based-on-extraoperative-electrocortical-stimulation-mapping</guid></item><item><title>当初神秘的“小红点”或许终于有了解释，感谢新发现的“小蓝同伴”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/mysterious-little-red-dots-at-the-beginning-time-may-finally-have-an-explanation-thanks-to-newfound-little-blue-companions</link><description>天文学家可能发现了神秘“小红点”的意想不到的起源，这种神秘“小红点”在詹姆斯·韦伯太空望远镜对早期宇宙的调查中似乎很常见。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mysterious-little-red-dots-at-the-beginning-time-may-finally-have-an-explanation-thanks-to-newfound-little-blue-companions.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 00:40:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/mysterious-little-red-dots-at-the-beginning-time-may-finally-have-an-explanation-thanks-to-newfound-little-blue-companions</guid></item><item><title>Dollar Tree商店中“傻瓜”袭击事件的增加令人不安：“他们觉得侮辱女性很有趣”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-disturbing-rise-of-gooner-assaults-at-dollar-tree-stores-they-find-it-funny-to-degrade-women</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 00:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-disturbing-rise-of-gooner-assaults-at-dollar-tree-stores-they-find-it-funny-to-degrade-women</guid></item><item><title>IRI 气候与社会研究所快速浏览</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/iri-institute-for-climate-and-society-quick-look</link><description>厄尔尼诺、拉尼娜和南方涛动状态的每月摘要，或&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/iri-institute-for-climate-and-society-quick-look2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 00:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/iri-institute-for-climate-and-society-quick-look</guid></item><item><title>耐酸纳米笼有望用于胃癌靶向治疗</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/acid-resistant-nanocage-shows-promise-for-targeted-gastric-cancer-therapy</link><description>新加坡国立大学杨潞龄医学院（NUS Medicine）的研究人员开发了一种可吞咽的纳米级递送平台，旨在通过胃的酸性环境运输治疗酶并激活肿瘤部位的抗癌反应。早期临床前研究结果表明，该方法可能提供一种更精确地治疗胃癌的新策略，同时减少对健康组织的损害。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/acid-resistant-nanocage-shows-promise-for-targeted-gastric-cancer-therapy2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:55:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/acid-resistant-nanocage-shows-promise-for-targeted-gastric-cancer-therapy</guid></item><item><title>天文学家在岩石世界 LHS 1140 b 上发现逸出的氦气</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/astronomers-find-escaping-helium-on-rocky-world-lhs-1140-b</link><description>通过探测逃逸到太空的氦气，天文学家首次发现了 LHS 1,140 b 上存在大气层的直接证据，LHS 1,140 b 是一颗位于其恒星宜居带的岩石系外行星。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/astronomers-find-escaping-helium-on-rocky-world-lhs-1140-b2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:40:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/astronomers-find-escaping-helium-on-rocky-world-lhs-1140-b</guid></item><item><title>Gemini架构直写芯片：谷歌全新AI推理芯片“Frozen v2”技术细节曝光，单位功耗处理能力提升高达10倍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/gemini-architecture-written-directly-into-silicon-technical-details-of-googles-new-ai-inference-chip-frozen-v2-revealed-processing-per-unit-of-power-consumption-increased</link><description>TradingKey — 据 The Information 援引两位知情人士的消息称，谷歌（GOOGL）正在开发一款新的服务器芯片，能够将 Gemini 大模型的底层架构直接嵌入到芯片硬件中，从而大幅提升用户 AI 服务的运行效率。这款内部代号为“Frozen v2”的AI推理芯片直接解决了谷歌目前AI算力严重不足的问题。消息人士透露，计算能力差距引发了内部资源冲突，甚至迫使谷歌云拒绝了众多外部客户的订单。研发团队预计，一旦该芯片正式部署，单位功耗处理的代币数量将是谷歌现有最新一代自研AI芯片的6至10倍。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gemini-architecture-written-directly-into-silicon-technical-details-of-googles-new-ai-inference-chip-frozen-v2-revealed-processing-per-unit-of-power-consumption-increased.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/gemini-architecture-written-directly-into-silicon-technical-details-of-googles-new-ai-inference-chip-frozen-v2-revealed-processing-per-unit-of-power-consumption-increased</guid></item><item><title>寿命延长专家 — AMA（第 1 部分）</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/lifespan-extension-expert-ama-pt-1</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/lifespan-extension-expert-ama-pt-1</guid></item></channel></rss>